data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT. SELLER WILL TAKE BACKUP OFFERS. Well maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bath updated townhome centrally located  in quiet neighborhood.  Unit is on the end for additional privacy. Seller has repainted exterior in Coastal colors . New flooring upstairs, new carpet upstairs. stairs have been repainted also, redone bathroom floors, sinks and light fixtures. Spacious kitchen with laundry room and WD hookups. Spacious backyard with partial privacy fence. Make an appt to see this one today!
